    <string>Right-click an account → Quick re-login… signs in inside the app instead of bouncing through Terminal and the browser.
Reuses your existing claude.ai web session so most accounts re-login in a single Authorize click.
The classic Terminal-based add-account flow is unchanged and still available as a one-click fallback.</string>
    <key>CBReleaseHotfixes</key>
