    <key>CBReleaseKnownIssues</key>
    <string>Quick re-login depends on Anthropic's authorize URL staying stable; if it ever fails, use the Terminal fallback button in the sheet.
Auto-swap does not kill the running `claude` process; enable Auto-kill CLI sessions to restart it automatically via claude-watch.
MCP hot-reload kills any in-flight Claude response and unsaved typed input — wait for idle before toggling MCP.</string>
